{"service_name": "Project, Programme & Portfolio Management (P3M)", "service_id": "5799419429519360", "company_name": "BMT Hi-Q Sigma Ltd", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     BMT Hi-Q Sigma Ltd\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Project, Programme &amp; Portfolio Management (P3M)\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Our comprehensive P3M service allows you to select from a range of targeted services or purchase an integrated end-to-end service. This enables you to manage Cloud and ICT project/programme/portfolio performance to deliver business benefits. We use recognised standards including APMP, Managing Successful Programmes (MSP), Management of Portfolios (MoP) and PRINCE2.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Integrated framework of processes, templates, guidance, tools and training documentation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Governance structures to support Cloud delivery, aligned with cultural environment\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Control of complex change and management of interdependencies\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Quantitative tracked costs and benefits management\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Comprehensive progress performance management reporting and communication\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Programme/project control systems integrated with business management systems\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Delivery plans directed towards achieving strategic objectives and business benefits\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Project specification aligned to project deliverables and programme outcomes\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Stakeholder analysis and engagement\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Ensures balanced investment across your Cloud portfolio, programmes and projects\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Builds the optimum portfolio of projects to achieve your objectives\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Enables informed, effective and robust decision making\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Achieves consistent information management approach across your organisation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Achieves consistent delivery approach across your organisation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Provides controlled integration of differing development approaches\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Increases stakeholder confidence in achieving desired outcomes and realising benefits\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     More accurate and efficient resource planning\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3468 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92598/5799419429519360-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92598/5799419429519360-sfia-rate-card.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SF